ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectMemorandum of Understanding between the Government of Canada and the Government of the United States of America concerning Cooperation on the Civil Lunar Gateway
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate the authority to sign, on behalf of Canada, and to bring into force for Canada, the MEMORANDUM OF UNDERSTANDING BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE GOVERNMENT OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA CONCERNING COOPERATION ON THE CIVIL LUNAR GATEWAY.
